ad_text: Banner Health Careers Sponsored Great nursing careers start with great training. New Graduate Nurse opportunities are available in Northern Colorado at Banner McKee Medical Center, Banner North Colorado Medical Center, and Banner Fort Collins Medical Center. Our program has received the highest accreditation by the American Nurses Credentialing Center (ANCC) as a Practice Transition Accreditation Program® (PTAP). Start your nursing career in a collaborative learning environment where you can refine your nursing skills, enhance your knowledge, and transition from a new graduate to a fully competent, professional nurse at Banner. Our culture makes the difference, we have a 91% retention rate for new graduates in Northern Colorado!
